high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the tub, turn right and face the tub to the left.
Pick up the green sponge on the edge of the tub behind the green curtain.
Turn around to face the sink.
Put the sponge inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn right and walk to the white dresser ahead.
Put the rinsed sponge on the dresser in front of the red towel.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed sponge on a dresser.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the bathtub on the other side of the room.
Pick up the green sponge from the front, right corner of the bathtub.
Turn around so that you are facing the sink right behind you.
Place the sponge in the sink, turn the water on, rinse out the sponge, turn the water off, and remove the sponge from the sink.
Turn to your right and go to the counter across the room.
Place the sponge on the counter, to the left of the box of tissue.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge on the counter.

high_descs: Go left and face the shower curtain hanging in front of the tub.
Pick the green sponge up from the side of the tub to the right of the shower curtain.
Turn around and face the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the sponge up again.
Cross the room and face the counter to the left of the tissue box.
Put the sponge on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge on the counter.
